Jobless and down on his luck, stock trader Jang Taesan was wandering aimlessly when he saw a speeding car racing toward a child. Though he saves the child’s life, he dies in the process. Reborn 14 years in the past, Taesan is a high schooler again, but he still remembers everything, including every top stock! With his family’s finances in tatters, it’s up to him to use his market foresight to change their fate. He may have failed in his past life, but this time his success will be legendary!
(Source: Tapas)

Aaron Steelegard's fortune was basically set as he discovered a book that allowed him to trade across dimensions—until his enemies take both his life and his riches away. But Aaron is brought back as his younger self, armed with his past knowledge and a chance at revenge! Now free to amass coins, he's gaining powerful abilities and moving up the ranks of the interdimensional trading markets. Will Aaron gain enough coins to survive this journey of vengeance and reclaim his honor? (Source: Tapas)
